{"tid":1489943,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港已經係危急存亡之際 9月後學生哥們weekend唔該唔好放棄","createTime":"2019-08-20T03:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T04:15:40.000Z","uid":112814,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a512867f5276b16c2ca27447f4efcdcbc3817f9","tid":1489943,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:48:51.000Z","msg":"818第三次百萬人大遊行 林奠依然拖字訣<br />\n黑警已經成為不可控既恐怖分子<br />\n相信係想等9月開學後佢地預算中既downturn<br />\n佢地睇死學生哥忙住番學 唔得閒出黎<br />\n我係度呼籲 undergrad既我知道9月唔會有太多assignment mid term，只不過會係一堆開學social<br />\n大學生我求下你地唔好放棄<br />\n中學生們請量力而為 weekend合法和理出到既我十分感謝<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分和勇 團結一心<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f14fe77ca53dfe65b4aa7851afb295af4244a342","tid":1489943,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:13:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f488199967990883893336bee4bd76a6c96f9d1","tid":1489943,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:14:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c437a08440df2004c2865c24a3f1573dbc5a433a","tid":1489943,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:15:02.000Z","msg":"821 822 823 824 831"},{"pid":"369ec5c087d738430fc0df8970203375891de584","tid":1489943,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:15:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eeec18e7610dc01c54be5794bf8a8a99bb642d2d","tid":1489943,"uid":285227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:15:40.000Z","msg":"push"}]}